hitch.body:
var me = {
    name: "Sam",
    greeting: function(){
        return "My name is: " + this.name;
    }
};

var greet = me.greeting; 
greet(); // returns "My name is " or whatever window.name is

slide_2.body:
    var greet = dojo.hitch( me, 'greeting' );

    greet(); // returns "My name is Sam"

Similar to Function.bind, _.bind etc.
